title: EU's Juncker speaks on Poland and Brexit
text:
EU's Juncker speaks on Poland and Brexit Wednesday, February 14, 2018 - 00:53 
European Commission President Jean-Claude Juncker says there's a ''good chance'' of rapprochement with Warsaw and insists he is not pushing for a 'European super-state'. Rough cut
